    'Travel from the ancient royal seat of Laos, through today’s laid back riverside capital of Vientiane and on to the amazing 4000 islands and waterfalls of southern Laos. This is a diverse, fully loaded-16 day city, culture, and nature lover’s tour with biking, trekking, and kayaking options throughout to keep you active as you explore Laos history, nature, and Buddhist culture.', '• UNESCO World Heritage Sites
