    '10 DAYS', 2024,
    'Embark on an unforgettable journey through NORTHERN LAOS IN STYLE. Experience the authentic culture, stunning landscapes, and warm hospitality of Laos. Your expert guide will take you off the beaten path for a truly immersive adventure.', '- Cruise up the Mekong River to explore the Pak Ou Cave of a thousand Buddhas
- Enjoy three nights and local excursions at the Namka Resort
