    27, 27, NULL, 'The Northern Loop',
    '4 DAYS', 1575,
    'The Classic Loop is an entry-level experience and can be shaped and honed for all riders, This excursion is a  great addition to an already existing tour and allows you to discover Laos at the perfect pace. 
The dramatic Karst Backdrop of Oudomxay province provides the canvas for a truly memorable ride. There are so many experiences packed into this shortish tour that your sense of wonder and adventure will be satisfied. form drifting along the mighty Mekong to zig-zagging downhill surrounded on either side by pristine forest. 
Nong Khiew is a delight with quiet riverside bars and restaurants and some unique trails and paths to rural communities untouched by tourism. 
The Northern Loop has everything!', 'Boat trip on Nam Ou
Spectacular Road Cycling 
Picnic Lunch on Slow Boat
Riverside Bungalows',
    'All sightseeing as described in the program above
Bike Hire, Helmets, Bags
3-night Village Homestay
1 Night Farmstay bungalow
English-speaking guide 
Entrance fees to the sights described above
Meals: B= breakfast, L= lunch, D= dinner
Lao PDR governmental tax and service charge
Luggage handling', 'All sightseeing as described in the program above
