INSERT INTO itineraries (id, tour_id, title, level, description, status, created_at)
VALUES (876, 36, 'Day 1: Luang Prabang City Bike Tour And Guided Meditation — Temple', 'easy', 'Luang Prabang City Bike Tour and Guided Meditation (L)
Our adventure begins early,  with a leisurely cycle through the sacred city, stopping by revered temples that hold centuries of wisdom to give alms to the Morning Monk Procession we return to the hotel for a light breakfast and a Yoga Session. Guided by our orange-robed instructors, immerse yourself in the mystique of monastic practices during an insightful temple tour. Prepare to embrace tranquillity as we gather for a one-hour guided meditation session, allowing you to find harmony amidst the serene surroundings.

Indulge in a delectable lunch at a local vocational training restaurant, a haven that empowers marginalized youth in the region. As our journey progresses, the breathtaking Mekong River beckons. Following our instructions, we''ll stroll along the Mekong''s edge, eventually joining a mesmerizing sunset cruise. Let the tranquil waters and vivid skies envelop you, marking the perfect culmination of a day filled with cultural exploration, inner reflection, and the sheer beauty of Luang Prabang. 

Yoga sessions 1-hour 
Meditation 1-hour 
Cycle 15 km 

Overnight in Luang Prabang', 'ACTIVE', NOW());
INSERT INTO itineraries (id, tour_id, title, level, description, status, created_at)
VALUES (877, 36, 'Day 2: Day Of Serenity And Adventure — Cave', 'moderate', 'Day of Serenity and Adventure: Embrace the Mekong''s Beauty(B, L)
Begin your day with a revitalising vinyasa flow yoga session, synchronising your breath with movement as the sun casts its early glow. Set against a serene backdrop, this invigorating practice prepares you for a day of exploration and tranquillity.
Embark on a cycling journey along the enchanting Mekong River. The gentle breeze and panoramic views accompany you as you pedal through quaint villages, lush landscapes, and traditional markets. The rhythmic cycling serves as a moving meditation, connecting you with the heartbeat of the land.
A picturesque boat ride awaits, guiding you to the sacred Pak Ou Caves. Nestled within towering limestone cliffs, these caves house thousands of Buddha statues, creating an awe-inspiring sanctuary. Immerse yourself in the hallowed grounds.
As the sun begins its descent, join us for a tranquil beach yoga session. Feel the soft sand beneath your feet as you engage in poses that harmonise your body and soul. 
Cycling 30km
Yoga 2 hour long sessions
Overnight in Pha An', 'ACTIVE', NOW());
INSERT INTO itineraries (id, tour_id, title, level, description, status, created_at)
VALUES (878, 36, 'Day 3: Serenity On The Nam Ou River And Adventure — Boat', 'moderate', 'Serenity on the Nam Ou River and Adventure(B, L)
Awaken your senses with a rejuvenating vinyasa yoga session on the tranquil beach, accompanied by the gentle caress of the cooling morning air. Let the rhythmic flow of your practice set the tone for another day of adventure and introspection.

Embark on a thrilling cycling expedition, covering 50 kilometres along the breathtaking Nam Ou River. Pedal through captivating landscapes, quaint villages, and scenic vistas. The journey is not just a physical endeavour, but a journey of connection with the land and yourself.
Indulge in the wonders of the Nam Ou Dam before embarking on a boat ride to the enchanting town of Nong Khiaw. Let the soothing ripples of the water and the stunning scenery guide you to this charming destination.
As the sun begins its descent, gather beneath the majestic limestone cliffs for an evening yoga session. The dramatic backdrop accentuates the serenity of your practice. 
Cycling 50km
Yoga 2 hour long sessions', 'ACTIVE', NOW());
INSERT INTO itineraries (id, tour_id, title, level, description, status, created_at)
VALUES (879, 36, 'Day 4: Waterfalls Trek — Waterfall', 'challenging', '100 waterfalls Trek (B,L)

After Morning Yoga Practice we will embark on a trekking expedition. Navigate through lush jungles, cascading streams, and rugged terrain as you journey to discover a hidden natural wonder. This trek takes you on an immersive adventure, passing by numerous waterfalls that cascade down dramatic cliffs. Traverse slippery rocks, climb bamboo ladders, and wade through crystal-clear pools. Each waterfall marks a triumph as you ascend higher into the breathtaking landscape. Feel the rush of adrenaline and the serenity of nature colliding, creating an unforgettable experience. Conquer the challenge, witness the mesmerizing falls, and create lasting memories on this daring exploration in the heart of Nong Khiaw. returning to the resort to unwind with a short evening yoga session 
Trek 3 hours 
No Cycling 
Yoga 2 hour long sessions', 'ACTIVE', NOW());
INSERT INTO itineraries (id, tour_id, title, level, description, status, created_at)
VALUES (880, 36, 'Day 5: Nong Khiaw — Bike', 'easy', 'Nong Khiaw - Nam Kat Yorla Pa Resort (B,L,D)
As the sun graces Nong Khiaw with its first rays, join us for a final invigorating Vinyasa yoga session, setting the tone for a day of remarkable exploration. After connecting body and mind, a thrilling adventure awaits.
We begin with a scenic 30-kilometer cycling journey from Nong Khiaw to Pakmong. Traverse picturesque landscapes, passing quaint villages and verdant fields. Every pedal stroke takes you closer to the heart of the province.
Transfer to a vantage point that offers a panoramic view from the roof of the province. Behold the sweeping vistas, an awe-inspiring testament to the natural beauty of Laos. Feel the harmony between the rugged terrain and your sense of adventure. We begin an exhilarating 30-kilometre descent on your bike, descending from the province''s roof into the vibrant city of Oudomxay. The wind rushes through your hair as you navigate this thrilling route, capturing the essence of freedom.
As the day gracefully evolves into the evening, relish a moment of calm during our sunset yoga session at the resort. Allow the serene atmosphere to guide your practice, embracing the tranquillity of dusk. Following your yoga session, indulge in a lavish local buffet dinner that celebrates the culinary richness of the region.

Yoga sessions 2-hour 
Cycle 60 km
Overnight in Namkat Yorla Pa Resort', 'ACTIVE', NOW());
INSERT INTO itineraries (id, tour_id, title, level, description, status, created_at)
VALUES (881, 36, 'Day 6: Nam Kat Yorla Pa Resort — Temple', 'moderate', 'Nam Kat Yorla Pa Resort- Pakbeng (B,L)
We continue our morning ritual and afternoon a healthy and energising yoga session we embark on the last cycle ride of our journey 
The route winds through lush landscapes, where emerald jungles and serene rivers create a picturesque backdrop. As you pedal along, the ever-changing panorama of rolling hills and verdant valleys unfolds before you, inviting you to savour each moment.
Cultural Encounters Along the Way: Engage with the heartwarming locals as you pass through quaint villages. Experience the genuine hospitality and authentic charm that Laos is renowned for, adding a layer of cultural enrichment to your journey.
Unveiling Hidden Gems: The route unveils hidden gems that encapsulate the essence of Laos, traditional markets, and ancient temples, each offering a unique glimpse into the country''s rich heritage.
Pakbeng''s Welcoming Embrace: Your adventure culminates in Pakbeng, a charming town on the banks of the Mekong River. 
Cycle 70km
Yoga sessions 2 hours 
Overnight in Pakbeng', 'ACTIVE', NOW());
INSERT INTO itineraries (id, tour_id, title, level, description, status, created_at)
VALUES (882, 36, 'Day 7: Slow Boat To Luang Prabang — Boat', 'moderate', 'Slow Boat to Luang Prabang 
After our final Yoga session of the tour, we step aboard the slow boat that cruises along the mighty Mekong River from Pak Beng to Luang Prabang. This leisurely journey promises a unique blend of serenity, panoramic vistas, and a deep connection with the heart of Laos.

Scenic Splendor Unveiled: Drift along the meandering Mekong, surrounded by breathtaking landscapes that transition from lush jungles to rugged cliffs. The unhurried pace of the boat allows you to immerse yourself in the tranquil beauty of the river''s banks and the ever-changing canvas of the horizon.
We end as we begin with a meditation session in a secluded monastery led by a senior Monk. 
Our cleansing quest for tranquillity in Laos is at an end. 
Overnight in Luang Prabang', 'ACTIVE', NOW());

