    41, 41, NULL, 'Hit The North',
    '10 DAYS', 2027,
    'Embark on an unforgettable journey through Hit The North. Experience the authentic culture, stunning landscapes, and warm hospitality of Laos. Your expert guide will take you off the beaten path for a truly immersive adventure.', '• UNESCO World Heritage Sites
• Expert English-speaking guide
• Authentic cultural experiences
• Small group, private service
• All entrance fees included',
    '- All sightseeing as described in the program above
- Transportation in private a /c vehicles
- Accommodation in hotels (twin shared)
- English-speaking biking guide 
- Admission fees to sights described above
- Meals: B= breakfast, L= lunch, D= dinner
