- Luggage handling
- Mountain bike rental and helmet including transport of bike', '- All sightseeing as described in the program above
- Transportation in private a /c vehicles
- Accommodation in hotels (twin shared)
- English-speaking biking guide 
- Admission fees to sights described above
- Meals: B= breakfast, L= lunch, D= dinner
