INSERT INTO itineraries (id, tour_id, title, level, description, status, created_at)
VALUES (1051, 43, 'Day 1: Luang Prabang — Market', 'easy', 'LUANG PRABANG (D)
Meet with our team for a short ride around Luang Prabang to ensure we are comfortable and confident for the journey ahead. We hold a short briefing before Dinner at a city centre Laos Restaurant, a charity for marginalised youth. (Khaiphaen Restaurant) to explain the Adventure ahead. After Dinner, you will have plenty of time to stroll through the Famous Night Market. 
 Overnight in Luang Prabang', 'ACTIVE', NOW());
INSERT INTO itineraries (id, tour_id, title, level, description, status, created_at)
VALUES (1052, 43, 'Day 2: Cycle Hike  To Kuang Si Waterfall — Waterfall', 'easy', 'CYCLE HIKE  TO KUANG SI WATERFALL 60 KM (B, L)
To day we transfer to a traditional Hmong Village and begin a 8 km hike to the magnificant falls 

Enjoy a swim in the clear water basins of the Kuang Si Waterfalls, a must-see for anyone visiting Laos. On the way back to the city, we will stop at Laos Buffalo Dairy for a tour of this incredible farm that supports local villages and educates in Animal welfare and husbandry. And also makes amazing Ice Cream; lunch is a picnic in the Farm''s Pagoda.

We will cycle back from the falls 

Overnight in Luang Prabang', 'ACTIVE', NOW());
INSERT INTO itineraries (id, tour_id, title, level, description, status, created_at)
VALUES (1053, 43, 'Day 3: Luang Prabang — Exploration', 'moderate', 'LUANG PRABANG – KASI 78 KM (B,L)
This day will probably be the most challenging tour, with two ascents of 15 and 24 kilometres. We''ll be cycling on winding roads with stunning views, passing hill tribe villages inhabited mainly by Hmong. 
Overnight in Kiu Katcham', 'ACTIVE', NOW());
INSERT INTO itineraries (id, tour_id, title, level, description, status, created_at)
VALUES (1054, 43, 'Day 4: Kasi — Exploration', 'moderate', 'KASI – PHOUKHOUN 55 KM & TRANSFER TO PHONSAVAN (B,L)
Today we will cycle between 1400 and 1000 metres up and down through small scenic valleys and over mountain ridges with stunning views. After lunch in Phou Khoun, we will have a transfer to Phonsavan, where the mysterious Plains of Jars are located. 
Overnight in Phonsavan', 'ACTIVE', NOW());
INSERT INTO itineraries (id, tour_id, title, level, description, status, created_at)
VALUES (1055, 43, 'Day 5: Round Trip To The Plain Of Jars — Exploration', 'moderate', 'ROUND TRIP TO THE PLAIN OF JARS 60km (B, L)
This is a perfect ride to get used to the new climate as we are over 1000 meters above sea level. The Plain of Jars remains a place whose mysterious past has led to diverse speculations. Why did people make these unique stone formations, and what were they used for? 
Overnight in Phonsavan', 'ACTIVE', NOW());
INSERT INTO itineraries (id, tour_id, title, level, description, status, created_at)
VALUES (1056, 43, 'Day 6: Phonsavan — Bike', 'moderate', 'PHONSAVAN – VIENGTHONG 98 KM (B, L)
After a 1 hr. transfer, we''ll start cycling through lovely scenery. We have to cross some passes that will reward us with great views. From Nam Neun, we''ll put the bikes back on the backup car and drive the last hour to Viengthong. Today''s ride is challenging with long Climbs. We stop by the hot springs outside of the town for a snack of boiled eggs and soy sauce.
Overnight in Viengthong.', 'ACTIVE', NOW());
INSERT INTO itineraries (id, tour_id, title, level, description, status, created_at)
VALUES (1057, 43, 'Day 7: Viengthong — Exploration', 'moderate', 'VIENGTHONG - VIENG KHAM 98 KM (B,L)
The day starts again with a short transfer to the highest point of today at 1200 meters above sea level. The fantastic landscapes will inspire you, so keep your camera ready – as we drop down into the small town of Vieng Kham. It''s just another wonderful biking day. A fantastic, spectacular ride with challenging ascents of 5-10km.
Overnight in Viengkham', 'ACTIVE', NOW());
INSERT INTO itineraries (id, tour_id, title, level, description, status, created_at)
VALUES (1058, 43, 'Day 8: Vieng Kham — Exploration', 'moderate', 'VIENG KHAM - NONG KHIAW 53 KM (B,L)
This day features some of the best mountain scenery on this trip. We start the day with a challenging ascent of 800 altitude meters. From the top of the mountain, it''s all downhill to the very scenic valley of Nong Khiaw, located on the banks of the Nam Ou. 
Overnight in Nong Khiaw', 'ACTIVE', NOW());
INSERT INTO itineraries (id, tour_id, title, level, description, status, created_at)
VALUES (1059, 43, 'Day 9: Waterfalls Trek — Waterfall', 'challenging', '100 Waterfalls Trek (B, L)
''Wow, wow, wow...'' is what the first travellers said after coming back from this amazing waterfall hike and river trip!!!
Starting the day with a peaceful boat ride on the Nam Ou you will be able to explore a small Lao village along the river side before heading into the waterfalls. Learn about their way of life along this river!
Walking through small streams and rice paddies, you arrive at the base of the 100 waterfalls. For the next few hours, you will see only water and jungle and hear the sound of clear waterfall cascades. The pools around you are very inviting for a refreshing splash.
Your guide will lead you through the cascades and prepare a local-style lunch on the falls in the middle of amazingly green nature...
A small villagers'' trail on the top of the 100 waterfalls will lead us back down into the valley, offering expansive views over the landscapes of the Nam Ou valley.
Overnight in Nong Khiaw', 'ACTIVE', NOW());
INSERT INTO itineraries (id, tour_id, title, level, description, status, created_at)
VALUES (1060, 43, 'Day 10: Nong Khiaw — Boat', 'moderate', 'NONG KHIAW – HUAI KAN (BOAT RIDE) - LUANG PRABANG (B,L)
The day starts with a relaxed 2-3 hour boat ride on the Nam Ou River, and enjoy the downstream journey with fine views of the limestone mountains. Next, we Cycle from the Dam along the riverside, calling at some bars and restaurants to cool off on our journey to Luang Prabang. 
Overnight in Luang Prabang', 'ACTIVE', NOW());
INSERT INTO itineraries (id, tour_id, title, level, description, status, created_at)
VALUES (1061, 43, 'Day 11: Luang Prabang — Exploration', 'moderate', 'LUANG PRABANG(B)
A free day to explore the ''Gem of South East Asia'' or perhaps A Lao Massage to ease the aching legs before departing for the Airport', 'ACTIVE', NOW());

-- ===== COUNTRY AND HIDDEN THAILAND ROUTE [BIKINGCYCLING (30)] =====
