    '14 days', 4330,
    'Embark on an unforgettable journey through Pakse to Siem Reap Cycle via 4000 Islands and Preah Vihear. Experience the authentic culture, stunning landscapes, and warm hospitality of Laos. Your expert guide will take you off the beaten path for a truly immersive adventure.', '• UNESCO World Heritage Sites
• Expert English-speaking guide
• Authentic cultural experiences
• Small group, private service
• All entrance fees included',
    '-All sightseeing as described in program above
-Bike Rental, Helmets and Locks
