- Souvenir  Cycle Jersey', '-All sightseeing as described in program above
-Bike Rental, Helmets and Locks
-Transportation in private a /c vehicles-
- 5 Nights Accommodation in hotels (Twin or Double)
- English speaking guide
 -Meals: B= breakfast, L= lunch, D= dinner
