    '14 days', 3635,
    'Embark on an unforgettable journey through Yunnan Breezes and Laos Trails. Experience the authentic culture, stunning landscapes, and warm hospitality of Laos. Your expert guide will take you off the beaten path for a truly immersive adventure.', 'Ancient Dali 
Vibrant Kunming markets 
Hill Tribes 
