VALUES (1239, 50, 'Day 14: Luang Prabang And Departure — Exploration', 'moderate', 'Luang Prabang and Departure (B)
We will escort you to the airport depending on your departure time', 'ACTIVE', NOW());

-- ===== LUANG PRABANG - NAMET NP - HALONG BAY [BIKINGCYCLING (30)] =====
