    '12 DAYS', NULL,
    'There are many tasks and activities for participants to do in the village, some essential to the jungle jar program and others vital to village life. We will break the group into small groups and rotate around the town, participating in many activities. These include; 
Bamboo weaving 
Roof Weaving 
Black smithery 
Rice growing/harvesting/planting 
Local style fishing 
Take care of domesticated animals
Eco brick construction using reclaimed plastic bottles. 
Cement mixing and bricklaying
Bamboo curing shaving, planting, and harvesting 
Making jungle jars in the village workshop', '• UNESCO World Heritage Sites
